bosh.js is a javascript library written on top of strophe.js

Features:
----------
1) multi-stream support
2) request and response ack
3) key sequence protection
4) support for long polling, chunked encoding, jsonp and websockets bosh requests
5) provide easy javascript development api which allows developer
   to not to focus on underlying xmpp protocol or it's working.
   Also implements a lot of functionalities/features to make 
   real-time frontend xmpp clients development fun